<section class="section" id="s-turnover">
<div class="stag">Protection Layer</div>
<div class="sh">The Turnover Shield</div>
<div class="sp">When someone gives notice, the system doesn't just say goodbye — it protects the knowledge that's about to walk out the door.</div>

<div class="sh" style="font-size:18px;margin-top:16px">Turnover Shield Process</div>

<div class="flow">
<div class="flow-node" style="border-color:var(--red-border);background:var(--red-bg)">🚨 Departure<br>Flagged</div>
<div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
<div class="flow-node">📊 Role<br>Assessment</div>
<div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
<div class="flow-node">⚠️ Gap<br>Analysis</div>
<div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
<div class="flow-node highlight">📝 Exit Interview<br>Template</div>
<div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
<div class="flow-node">🗣️ Knowledge<br>Extraction</div>
<div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
<div class="flow-node security">📚 SOPs Created<br>& Published</div>
</div>

<div class="grid-2">
<div class="card">
<div class="card-h">📊 What the Assessment Does</div>
<div class="card-p">When a departure is flagged, the AI cross-references the person's role against the knowledge base:</div>
<table class="tbl">
<tr><th>Check</th><th>What It Looks For</th></tr>
<tr><td>SOP Coverage</td><td>How many of the role's processes have documented SOPs?</td></tr>
<tr><td>Sole Ownership</td><td>Which SOPs were created only by this person (no co-authors)?</td></tr>
<tr><td>Stale Content</td><td>Which SOPs were last updated >6 months ago and may be outdated?</td></tr>
<tr><td>Undocumented Knowledge</td><td>What processes does this role handle that have NO SOP at all?</td></tr>
<tr><td>Tribal Knowledge Signals</td><td>Meeting notes where this person was the primary responder on questions</td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="card-h">📝 Exit Interview Generator</div>
<div class="card-p">The AI generates a structured interview template specific to the departing employee:</div>
<div class="callout" style="margin-top:10px"><strong>Example output for Sarah (Insurance Verification Specialist, 4 years):</strong><br><br>
"9 processes tied to Sarah's role have no documented SOP. The following questions are designed to extract this knowledge before her last day:<br><br>
1. Pre-authorization: Walk me through how you determine which payers need pre-auth. Are there exceptions?<br>
2. Aetna secret line: You mentioned a direct number that bypasses the automated system. What is it and when should we use it?<br>
3. Denial appeals: What's your step-by-step process when a claim is denied? Any payer-specific tricks?<br>
..."</div>
</div>
</div>
